\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs28 Time of Dhuhr:\par
\b0\fs22 The start of the time for Dhuhr is when the sun has passed its zenith i.e., has passed the highest part of the sky and started to descend towards the west, and it lasts until the shadow of everything is equal in length to the object itself, plus the length of the shadow of the object at the time of the zenith.\par

